## Phase 1 Implementation Plan

### What we're building
User registers → auto-creates org → sets up 2FA → logs in → sees empty dashboard. All mutations audit-logged.

### File Structure
```
src/
  app/
    (auth)/
      login/page.tsx
      register/page.tsx
      forgot-password/page.tsx
      reset-password/page.tsx
